OL,3,CZuckerberg announces changes to fact
OL,4,Cchecking on-Meta - what will it look
OL,5,Clike?
OL,7,FIn a new Trumpian era of a free for
OL,8,Fall on social media, Mr Zuckerberg
OL,9,Fsays he's getting rid of fact checkers
OL,10,Fat Instagram and Facebook, starting in
OL,11,Fthe United States. He cited free
OL,12,Fexpression as the reason, as ITV News
OL,13,FScience Editor Martin Stew reports.
OL,15,FMark Zuckerberg has announced a series
OL,16,Fof changes to content moderation and
OL,17,Ffact-checking on Meta, raising concern
OL,18,Famong online safety campaigners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
