OL,3,CZuckerberg announces changes to fact
OL,4,Cchecking on-Meta - what will it look
OL,5,Clike?
OL,7,FMeta's chief executive says he hopes
OL,8,Fto "get back to our roots" and restore
OL,9,F"free expression on our platforms".
OL,11,FThe changes will affect Facebook and
OL,12,FInstagram, the company's two largest
OL,13,Fsocial media platforms which have
OL,14,Fbillions of users, as well as its
OL,15,Fnewer platform Threads.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
