OL,3,CZuckerberg announces changes to fact
OL,4,Cchecking on-Meta - what will it look
OL,5,Clike?
OL,7,FSome of the changes include the
OL,8,Freplacement of fact-checkers with
OL,9,Fcommunity notes, the removal of
OL,10,Frestrictions on topics that are the
OL,11,Fsubject of frequent political debate,
OL,12,Fand an increasing reliance on users to
OL,13,Freport policy violations.
OL,15,F"We're going to get back to our roots
OL,16,Fand focus on reducing mistakes,
OL,17,Fsimplifying our policies and restoring
OL,18,Ffree expression on our platforms," Mr
OL,19,FZuckerberg said in a video.
