OL,7,FSo what are the changes being
OL,8,Fannounced?
OL,10,FReplacement of fact-checkers with
OL,11,Fcommunity notes
OL,13,FMr Zuckerberg said Meta will get rid
OL,14,Fof fact-checkers and "replace them
OL,15,Fwith community notes similar to X."
OL,17,FAs a result, Meta will rely on users
OL,18,Fto add notes to posts that might be
OL,19,Ffalse or misleading, instead of using
OL,20,Fnews organisations or other third-
OL,21,Fparty groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
