OL,3,CZuckerberg announces changes to fact
OL,4,Cchecking on-Meta - what will it look
OL,5,Clike?
OL,7,FIt will be rolled out in the US over
OL,8,Fthe next few months.
OL,10,F"It means that we're going to catch
OL,11,Fless bad stuff, but we'll also reduce
OL,12,Fthe number of innocent people's posts
OL,13,Fand accounts that we accidentally take
OL,14,Fdown," Mr Zuckerberg said.
OL,16,FHe said that after Trump was elected
OL,17,Fin 2016, the "legacy media wrote non-
OL,18,Fstop about how misinformation was a
OL,19,Fthreat to democracy" and that Meta
OL,20,Ftried to address the concerns without
OL,21,F"becoming the arbiters of truth."
OL,26,@rD@AOU
