OL,7,F"But the fact-checkers have just been
OL,8,Ftoo politically biased and have
OL,9,Fdestroyed more trust than they've
OL,10,Fcreated, particularly in the US," Mr
OL,11,FZuckerberg said.
OL,13,FThe policy signals a move towards a
OL,14,Fmore conservative-leaning focus on
OL,15,Ffree speech by Mr Zuckerberg, who met
OL,16,FDonald Trump in November after he won
OL,17,Fthe US election.
