OL,8,Fplease the president-elect, who
OL,9,Fcriticised Meta's fact-checking
OL,10,Ffeature for penalising conservative
OL,11,Fvoices.
OL,13,FMeta donated a million dollars to
OL,14,Fsupport Mr Trump's inauguration in
OL,15,FDecember, and has since appointed
OL,16,Fseveral Trump allies to high-ranking
OL,17,Fpositions at the firm.
OL,19,FThe demoting of fact-checked posts
OL,20,Fwill be stopped
