OL,7,FMr Kaplan said Meta would also begin
OL,8,Floosening some of its rules around
OL,9,Fcontent moderation, saying it wanted
OL,10,Fto "undo the mission creep that has
OL,11,Fmade our rules too restrictive and too
OL,12,Fprone to over-enforcement".
OL,14,FHe said the site would "remove
OL,15,Frestrictions" on topics that are the
OL,16,Fsubject of frequent political debate `
OL,17,Fincluding immigration, gender identify
OL,18,Fand gender ` adding that it was "not
OL,19,Fright" that things could be said on
OL,20,Fthe floor of the US Congress but not
OL,21,Fon Meta platforms.
