OL,7,FHe confirmed Meta would continue to
OL,8,Fuse automated systems for "illegal and
OL,9,Fhigh-severity violations", such as
OL,10,Fterrorism, child sexual exploitation,
OL,11,Fdrugs, fraud and scams, but said
OL,12,Fautomated moderation had resulted in
OL,13,F"too many mistakes and too much
OL,14,Fcontent being censored".
OL,16,FWhat is the reaction to the changes?
OL,18,FOne online safety charity said it was
OL,19,F"dismayed" by the decision.
