OL,7,FIan Russell, chairman of the Molly
OL,8,FRose Foundation (MRF), said the
OL,9,Fdecision was a "major concern for
OL,10,Fsafety online".
OL,12,FThe MRF was set up by Mr Russell and
OL,13,Fhis family in memory of his daughter,
OL,14,Fwho killed herself aged 14 in November
OL,15,F2017 after viewing harmful content on
OL,16,Fsocial media.
