OL,7,F"We are dismayed that the company
OL,8,Fintends to stop proactive moderation
OL,9,Fof many forms of harmful content and
OL,10,Fto only act if and when a user
OL,11,Fcomplaint is received," Mr Russell
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"Meta currently claims the
OL,15,Foverwhelming majority of harmful
OL,16,Fmaterial they remove is found by
OL,17,Fthemselves rather than reported by
OL,18,Fusers.
