OL,7,F"We are urgently clarifying the scope
OL,8,Fof these measures, including whether
OL,9,Fthis will apply to suicide, self-harm
OL,10,Fand depressive content.
OL,12,F"These moves could have dire
OL,13,Fconsequences for many children and
OL,14,Fyoung adults."
OL,16,FUK fact-checking charity Full Fact
OL,17,Fsaid the decision was likely to help
OL,18,Fmisinformation more easily spread
OL,19,Fonline.
