OL,7,FChris Morris, chief executive of Full
OL,8,FFact, said: "Meta's decision to end
OL,9,Fits partnership with fact checkers in
OL,10,Fthe US is disappointing and a
OL,11,Fbackwards step that risks a chilling
OL,12,Feffect around the world.
OL,14,F"From safeguarding elections to
OL,15,Fprotecting public health to
OL,16,Fdissipating potential unrest on the
OL,17,Fstreets, fact checkers are first
OL,18,Fresponders in the information
OL,19,Fenvironment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
