OL,7,F"Our specialists are trained to work
OL,8,Fin a way that promotes credible
OL,9,Fevidence and prioritises tackling
OL,10,Fharmful information - we believe the
OL,11,Fpublic has a right to access our
OL,12,Fexpertise.
OL,14,FSocial media expert Matt Navarra said
OL,15,FMeta's approach could also be part of
OL,16,Fbroader efforts from tech firms
OL,17,Fpushing back against international
OL,18,Fregulation.
