OL,8,Fregions such as the EU have begun
OL,9,Fintroducing regulations for social
OL,10,Fmedia platforms for the first time,
OL,11,Fand new competition laws are also
OL,12,Flooking to curb the power of big US
OL,13,Ftech firms.
