OL,7,F"I think Zuckerberg isn't shy about
OL,8,Fthe political motivations behind the
OL,9,Fmove, because in his statement he
OL,10,Fcriticises the governments outside the
OL,11,FUS, including in Europe, saying Europe
OL,12,Fis institutionalising censorship -
OL,13,Fthis language signals a broader fight
OL,14,Fagainst international regulation," Mr
